    "ChatGPT is built on the probabilities of linguistic sequences found in the corpus of texts.",
    "Thus, it can acquire practical semantics or grammatical structure without explicit instruction.",
    "It also learns verbal associations-some of which may be objectionable, unless carefully monitored and mitigated (e.g.",
    "Beyond simple associations it acquires high-level abstractions like expressive structure, ideology or belief systems, since these are all manifested in the corpora that make up its training sets.",
